HEADWORD: Unconstant
<hw>Un*con"stant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not constant;
inconstant; fickle; changeable.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <au>Shak.</au>
-- <wordforms><wf>Un*con"stant*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> -- <wf>Un*con"stant*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unconstitutional</ent>⟦br⟧
